<view class="page-shell index-page">
  <view class="hero">
    <view class="hero-hint">
      <text class="hint-label">提示</text>
      <text class="hint-copy">选择太阳星座，查看今日或本周行运。</text>
    </view>
    <text class="title">观星日课Lite</text>
    <text class="subtitle">Western Tropical Astrology</text>
  </view>

  <view class="period-tabs">
    <button
      class="period-tab {{period === 'daily' ? 'active' : ''}}"
      data-period="daily"
      bindtap="selectPeriod"
    >
      今日运势
    </button>
    <button
      class="period-tab {{period === 'weekly' ? 'active' : ''}}"
      data-period="weekly"
      bindtap="selectPeriod"
    >
      本周运势
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">选择星座</view>
    <view class="sign-grid">
      <button
        wx:for="{{signs}}"
        wx:key="key"
        class="sign-card element-{{item.elementKey}}"
        data-sign="{{item.key}}"
        bindtap="openDetail"
      >
        <text class="sign-icon">{{item.icon}}</text>
        <view class="sign-copy">
          <text class="sign-name">{{item.cn}}</text>
          <text class="sign-meta">{{item.en}} · {{item.range}}</text>
        </view>
        <text class="sign-element">{{item.element}}</text>
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="star-footer">
    <text>十二星座各有潮汐，愿你在今日星光里与自己相逢。</text>
  </view>
</view>
